  <h1>
   mouse_lastbutton
  </h1>
  This variable returns the last mouse button that was pressed and can return any of the special
  <a href="Mouse_Input.htm">
   mouse constants
  </a>
  except
  <span>
   mb_any
  </span>
  (you may also set this variable to one of the constants).
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">mouse_lastbutton;
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml"><a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Game_Input/Mouse_Input/mouse_check_button.htm">
 Mouse Button Constant
</a>
(except mb_any)
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">if mouse_lastbutton = mb_left
{
    x -= 1;
}
</code></pre>
  This moves the current instance left if the last button pressed was the left mouse button.
 </body>
